    • registerFutureVertexForPrefetching

      public void registerFutureVertexForPrefetching​(org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Vertex futureVertex)
      从接口复制的说明: MultiQueriable
      Registers a vertex which will pass this step at some point in the future. The vertex is typically known because a traverser at that vertex location has passed a previous step earlier. Using that information, a step can know in advance a set of vertices which it will have to handle in the future.
      指定者:
      registerFutureVertexForPrefetching 在接口中 MultiQueriable<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element,​E>
      参数:
      futureVertex - The vertex which will reach the step in the future.

    • ensureAdditionalHasContainersCapacity

      public void ensureAdditionalHasContainersCapacity​(int additionalSize)
      从接口复制的说明: HasStepFolder
      Optional method which provides a hint to future has containers additions. The method will optionally resize the underlying array for future addition to ensure that it can hold additional elements. I.e. it will ensure that we can add `additionalSize` containers without any resizes.
      指定者:
      ensureAdditionalHasContainersCapacity 在接口中 HasStepFolder<org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element,​E>
